(1859, 'en', NULL, 'phpfox', NULL, 'setting_user_profile_private_age', '<title>Force Profile Privacy</title><info>Define what age should a users profile be forced to be private regardless of their profile privacy setting.\r\n\r\nIf the user\'s age is the same or lower than the setting, only their friends will be able to see their profile and interact with them.\r\n\r\n<b>Notice:</b> Set to \"0\" (without quotes) for no limit.</info>', '<title>Force Profile Privacy</title><info>Define what age should a users profile be forced to be private regardless of their profile privacy setting.\r\n\r\nIf the user\'s age is the same or lower than the setting, only their friends will be able to see their profile and interact with them.\r\n\r\n<b>Notice:</b> Set to \"0\" (without quotes) for no limit.</info>', 1599831384),
